Best gluten free friendly restaurant in the city! Anthony, the owner, is dedicated to amazing food and safe allergy environment. The food is amazing and seasonal, servers knowledgable and the service is excellent. Dessert here is something to talk about including melt in your mouth cheesecake, red velvet cake with cream cheese frosting, and carrot cake with nuts all gluten free! Extensive wine list and drinks menu. Call for reservations, this is a must for all those with Celiac!
